{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"FileReader.readAsText()","mdn_url":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/FileReader/readAsText","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/File_API\">File API <small>(en-US)</small></a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/FileReader\"><code>FileReader</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Construtor</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/FileReader/FileReader\"><code>FileReader()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Propriedades</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileReader/error\"><code>error</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileReader/readyState\"><code>readyState</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileReader/result\"><code>result</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Métodos</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileReader/abort\"><code>abort()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/FileReader/readAsArrayBuffer\"><code>readAsArrayBuffer()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/FileReader/readAsBinaryString\"><code>readAsBinaryString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/FileReader/readAsDataURL\"><code>readAsDataURL()</code></a></li><li><em><code>readAsText()</code></em></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Eventos</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileReader/abort_event\"><code>abort</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileReader/error_event\"><code>error</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/FileReader/load_event\"><code>load</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileReader/loadend_event\"><code>loadend</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileReader/loadstart_event\"><code>loadstart</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileReader/progress_event\"><code>progress</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Herança:</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Páginas relacionadas a File API</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Blob\"><code>Blob</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/File\"><code>File</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/FileList\"><code>FileList</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileReaderSync\"><code>FileReaderSync</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/URL/createObjectURl\"><code>URL.createObjectURL()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/URL/revokeObjectURL\"><code>URL.revokeObjectURL()</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p>O método readAsText é usado para ler conteúdos de um <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Blob\"><code>Blob</code></a> ou <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/File\"><code>File</code></a> especificados. Quando a operação de leitura é concluida, o <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileReader/readyState\"><code>readyState</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> é alterado para DONE, o <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest/loadend_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">loadend (en-US)</a></code> é disparado, e o atributo <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileReader/result\"><code>result</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> passa a conter o conteúdo do arquivo como um texto em formato string.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sintaxe","title":"Sintaxe","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><em>instanceOfFileReader</em>.readAsText(blob[, encoding]);</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parâmetros","title":"Parâmetros","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"blob\"><code>blob</code></dt>\n <dd>O <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Blob\"><code>Blob</code></a> ou <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/File\"><code>File</code></a> a ser lido.</dd>\n <dt id=\"encoding\">encoding <span class=\"badge inline optional\">Optional</span></dt>\n <dd>Uma string especificando a codificação a ser usada para o dado retornado. Por padrão, UTF-8 é assumido se o parâmetro não for especificado.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"especificações","title":"Especificações","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Especificação</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comentário</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/FileAPI/#FileReader-interface\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">File API<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'FileReader' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">Rascunho atual</span></td>\n   <td>Definição inicial</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility","title":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect2\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Estamos convertendo nossos dados de compatibilidade para o formato JSON</a></strong>.\n            Esta tabela de compatibilidade ainda usa o formato antigo,\n            pois ainda não convertemos os dados que ela contém.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Descubra como você pode ajudar! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect3\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Dispositivo móvel</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Edge</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Suporte básico</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/3.6\" title=\"Released on 2010-01-21.\">3.6</a> (1.9.2)<sup>[1]</sup></td>\n   <td>7</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td>10<sup>[2]</sup></td>\n   <td>12.02<sup>[3]</sup></td>\n   <td>6.0.2</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Edge</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Suporte básico</td>\n   <td>32</td>\n   <td>3</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td>10</td>\n   <td>11.5</td>\n   <td>6.1</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<p>[1] Antes do&nbsp;Gecko 2.0 beta 7 (Firefox 4.0 beta 7), todos os parâmetros&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Blob\"><code>Blob</code></a> abaixo eram parâmetros de <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/File\"><code>File</code></a>; isso desde então foi atualizado para coincidir com a especificação corretamente.&nbsp;Antes do&nbsp;Gecko 13.0 (Firefox 13.0 / Thunderbird 13.0 / SeaMonkey 2.10) a propriedade <code>FileReader.error</code>&nbsp;retornava um objeto&nbsp;<a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"A documentação sobre isto ainda não foi escrita; por favor considere contribuir!\"><code>FileError</code></a>. Essa interface foi removida e agora <code>FileReader.error</code>&nbsp;está retornando um objeto <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMError\"><code>DOMError</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> conforme definido no&nbsp;último rascunho da FileAPI.</p>\n\n<p>[2] IE9 tem uma&nbsp;<a href=\"http://html5labs.interoperabilitybridges.com/prototypes/fileapi/fileapi/info\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">File API Lab</a>.</p>\n\n<p>[3] Opera tem <a href=\"https://www.opera.com/docs/specs/presto28/file/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">suporte parcial</a>&nbsp;em 11.1.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"veja_também","title":"Veja também","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/FileReader\"><code>FileReader</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Sintaxe","id":"sintaxe"},{"text":"Especificações","id":"especificações"},{"text":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"Veja também","id":"veja_também"}],"summary":"O método readAsText é usado para ler conteúdos de um Blob ou File especificados. Quando a operação de leitura é concluida, o readyState (en-US) é alterado para DONE, o loadend (en-US) é disparado, e o atributo result (en-US) passa a conter o conteúdo do arquivo como um texto em formato string.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"FileReader.readAsText()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"FileReader.readAsText()","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"FileReader.readAsText()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"FileReader.readAsText()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"FileReader.readAsText()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"FileReader.readAsText()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"FileReader.readAsText()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/api/filereader/readastext","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/api/filereader/readastext/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API","title":"APIs da Web"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/FileReader","title":"FileReader"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/FileReader/readAsText","title":"FileReader.readAsText()"}],"pageTitle":"FileReader.readAsText() - APIs da Web | MDN","noIndexing":false}}